[


  Program lćs

  Read reals to help3 area at RC2000 speed

  Only digits and minus are accepted. Case shifts and blanks are ignored.
  Reading stops at STOP CODE or ĺ.
  The last number of a track is a or b marked, the very last number c marked.


  Indicator:
  OA 512
  OB 256
  TA 128
  TB  64        0: buffer 1, 1: buffer 2
  PA  32	Finished
  PB  16	checksumming
  QA   8	End of buffer 1
  QB   4        End of buffer 2
  RA   2        Negative
  RB   1        . met
]
_b k=d1,i=40d13,a60,b20
